oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Real photo post card of communication tent in Ourches, France and communication team from 90th Aero Squadron
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This photograph shows the communication tent in Ourches, France and communication team from 90th Aero Squadron. The cards was sent by Cpl. John Shannon Garrett. He writes, "This is our radio station during the St. Mihiel drive" and "Corp. Garrett is under the x." Garrett worked in the 90th Aero Squadron repairing, installing, and maintaining the radios in the planes and the radio station.
